{"tid":1870734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港龍工會獲授權隨時罷工","createTime":"2020-02-09T04:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T06:35:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e0adb36b40397c5258d67b4051fb4115e9fd99","tid":1870734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200209/ORETNLYFXDE7OM4WUH6BRMEQSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200209%2FORETNLYFXDE7OM4WUH6BRMEQSY%2F&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=52a60b4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200209%2FORETNLYFXDE7OM4WUH6BRMEQSY%2F&h=d6e88c79\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200209/ORETNLYFXDE7OM4WUH6BRMEQSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n港龍工會獲授權隨時罷工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200209/large/1581179986_2751.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200209%2Flarge%2F1581179986_2751.jpg&h=ba974361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施安娜（中）等昨主持港龍工會大會。 謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港龍空勤人員協會昨舉行特別會員大會，表決通過授權工會發動罷工行動。因未能取得總會員人數超過一半簽署，故擱置今日起一連三日的罷工。然而，由於會員已授權工會發起工業行動，故工會可隨時發動罷工，毋須再召開大會。工會將於今午2時先在東涌舉行集會，收集會員意見。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：隔離夫婦對港府hea做感洩氣<br />\n<br />\n港龍空勤人員協會昨開會員大會，約200人出席。會上討論疫情相關事項，並進行投票，授權工會發動工業行動。投票結果以420票贊成、22票反對及25張廢票下，通過授權工會發動罷工行動。協會總幹事施安娜表示，大會上已向會員清楚解釋，罷工是合法的工業行動，非國泰港龍航空行政總裁丘應樺威脅指是違法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200209/large/1581179985_b416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200209%2Flarge%2F1581179985_b416.jpg&h=f1d62504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會員表決通過授權工會發動罷工行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三連罷未能通過<br />\n<br />\n對於另一「投名狀」投票，因未能取得逾半數人簽署，故未能通過今日起一連三日預告式罷工。施認為因時間倉卒，會員對投名狀及罷工也未太了解，加上受資方威嚇，可能因而卻步，但強調會員有罷工決心，這星期每天約有400人請病假，可見員工對疫情的憂慮及對公司的不滿。日後工會可隨時發起工業行動，包括罷工，「更加畀到公司一個有效打擊」。<br />\n<br />\n國泰及港龍近月接連有乘客確診武漢肺炎，其中港龍至少有六名機組人員因此而被送往隔離營，另有多名員工也要接受家居檢疫，惟港龍遲遲才准許機組人員戴口罩執勤，但拒絕全面停飛內地線，保護物資供不應求。國泰行政總裁鄧健榮發出電郵，表明對工會擬發起罷工感失望，又指工會行動具破壞性，對其他員工不公平，盼工會重新考慮，避免對公司的業務造成任何干擾，及對乘客及員工造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王家文"},{"pid":"2795ace32b35e0aaee71fb2aebd45a4f3f8b783f","tid":1870734,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T04:59:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d99ed7a93ae96f3e55978a2bf75c7335577d038c","tid":1870734,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"因龍加油"},{"pid":"cec3514fb6059a895bb4e7ba014939976633de26","tid":1870734,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:30:20.000Z","msg":"隨時罷"},{"pid":"914438fe4043339830a1aeb09edde626e0066519","tid":1870734,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:32:51.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"419dae38cbb007a3941ca82cb11a6db81ed5af1d","tid":1870734,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"施安娜女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0712ca961ba31caa04d5cf3119b38e22ea00327c","tid":1870734,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:33:41.000Z","msg":"而家罷"},{"pid":"f470c6f3e944a753f8c5efd30937febc499a3382","tid":1870734,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"【獨媒直播】空勤人員要求封關集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inmediahknet/videos/603444556884228/?v=603444556884228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finmediahknet%2Fvideos%2F603444556884228%2F%3Fv%3D603444556884228&d=CEXeqV9R6719hdRRqmVjOv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=8e457cf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inmediahknet/videos/603444556884228/?v=603444556884228</a>"},{"pid":"cc5a9b8c0ecd0169bf7c6ea4d85aa231c1278bcc","tid":1870734,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T06:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}